These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, 7up, water, coffee
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the russian is between the person drinking coffee and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | coffee | water | 7up    | sprite  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

