.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, german, italian, thai, turkish
House: victorian, palace, wooden, gothic-revival, art-deco, farmhouse
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the thai##1
3. the gothic-revival house is between the italian and the argentine##2
4. the german is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the art-deco house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the italian is on the right of the victorian house##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | thai | italian | german | argentine  |
| House           | farmhouse | art-deco  | victorian | palace    | gothic-revival  | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, egyptian, canadian, russian, indian, thai
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the indian##1
3. the turkish is on the left of the russian##1
4. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the turkish##2
7. the egyptian is on the far left##1
8. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | snake      | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog      |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | thai  | turkish | russian   | indian       | canadian |

