House: palace, cape-cod, colonial, art-deco, tower, farmhouse
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
7. the palace house is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | satire    | western | family | drama | sports   |
| House         | tower | palace | colonial | farmhouse | art-deco  | cape-cod |

