.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, disco, electronic, country, classical
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of blues##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of classical##1
8. the fan of disco is between the fan of electronic and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the fan of dubstep is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Music-Genre    | dubstep | classical | country  | electronic      | disco | blues  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

