.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, cooking, gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, tulip, azalea, bellflower, aconite
1. the person who growsazalea is the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsbellflower##2
7. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | hiking | chess | reading | gardening | cooking |
| Flower   | tulip | aconite    | bellflower  | begonia    | azalea    | zinnia    |

