.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  designer, journalist, mechanic, musician, social-worker, teacher
The people have 6 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing, cooking, gardening, hiking, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
4. the musician is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the mechanic is between the journalist and the social-worker##2
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | musician | teacher | social-worker | mechanic | journalist | designer |
| Hobby   | cooking   | gardening   | rock-climbing         | traveling    | woodworking     | hiking     |

