.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, singing, sudoku
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, trike, train, scooter, motorbike, quad-bike
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person driving the boat is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 3. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Transport   | trike | boat | quad-bike    | motorbike | scooter | train |

