1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person traveling to paris is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching family movies and the person traveling to colone##2
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1

