.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, dunhill, aristoff, old-henry, game
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, skateboard, subway, train, van
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the train##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the jet-ski and the dunhill-smoker##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is the person driving the car##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is between the person driving the car and the prince-smoker##2
10. the aristoff-smoker is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar         | game   | old-henry | dunhill       | aristoff | alhambra    | prince |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train  | skateboard | car      | subway | van        |

