.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, cherry, cranberry, kale, peas, pineapple
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: horror, western, comedy, martial-arts, family, sports
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is between the person eating peas and the person eating kale##2
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating apple##1
8. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Food          | cranberry | cherry | apple | peas    | pineapple | kale |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | sports | martial-arts   | western | horror | family |

