.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There 6 different types of food: avocado, banana, mango, onion, peas, zucchini
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, begonia, aconite, zinnia, daffodil
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growszinnia and the person eating banana##2
 3. the person who growszinnia is between the person eating zucchini and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is between the person who growsbegonia and the person eating mango##2
 6. the person eating onion is the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Food   | onion     | avocado | peas   | mango     | zucchini       | banana       |
| Flower    | dahlia | aconite   | balloon-flower | zinnia | daffodil | begonia |

