.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
6 different games are played: whist, bridge, scrabble, poker, billiard, backgammon
There are 6 different nationalities: british, chinese, dutch, italian, russian, turkish
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the british is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the italian is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
 6. the turkish is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the chinese is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the russian is on the right of the british##1
 9. the dutch is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing whist##2
10. the person playing billiard is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Game         | poker | whist | bridge | backgammon | billiard | scrabble |
| Nationality   | british | russian | dutch      | italian     | turkish       | chinese |

 